text: Amit Mishra (born 11 November 1991) is an Indian cricketer who plays for Uttar Pradesh cricket team in domestic cricket. He is a right-arm Medium-Fast bowler who was a member of the Rajasthan Royals squad for 2014 Indian Premier League.
